sertions**\\n\\nOkay, I'm thinking about checkstyle. Not using assertThat(isAvailable).isTrue seems fine. However, if the native UnsupportedFeatureError in ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe.isAvailable is caught, then I wonder what happens if isAvailable returns false and is not caught. It could occur on Native due to GraalImageCode, but since we already set it to false, I need to double-check how this impacts everything. These details are crucial for ensuring proper functionality.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering class loading issues**\\n\\nI'm thinking about a potential issue with importing DynamicType from a shaded package. It's crucial to check if the class is already loaded due to possible collisions with the system loader. I'll look into using URLClassLoader as a parent test class loader to see if the class has been loaded anywhere. I also need to think about the unique package generation and how injection into URLClassLoader works, especially since it may lead to defined package issues or lacking a Package object.\"}]}"}, {"type": "text", "text": "Implemented a focused test for the active dynamic-access class.\n\nAdded:\n\n- `tests/src/io.projectreactor.tools/blockhound/1.0.8.RELEASE/src/test/java/io_projectreactor_tools/blockhound/ClassInjectorInnerUsingUnsafeInnerDispatcherInnerCreationActionTest.java`\n\nWhat it does:\n\n- Uses BlockHound’s shaded Byte Buddy public API.\n- Forces `net.bytebuddy.safe=false` before first `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe` access.\n- Calls `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe.isAvailable()` to trigger `Dispatcher.CreationAction.run()`.\n- Injects a generated class into an isolated `URLClassLoader` through `ClassInjector.UsingUnsafe`, exercising the initialized dispatcher.\n- Handles Native Image unsupported dynamic class loading via `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)`.\n\nI did not run compile/tests, per instruction.\n\nNote: the working tree already had unrelated modifications in:\n\n- `tests/src/io.projectreactor.tools/blockhound/1.0.8.RELEASE/src/test/java/io_projectreactor_tools/blockhound/NexusAccessorInnerDispatcherInnerCreationActionTest.java`\n\nI did not edit that file.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07bf651027454a01016a29362e523081948058698f71fd0825\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1121, "output": 1737, "cacheRead": 32768, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 35626, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1781085700423, "responseId": "resp_07bf651027454a01016a293604f6488194b8c1510f74e5248d"}, "toolResults": []}
